---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Section from "../components/Section.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Our Story" noindex description="Discover the story behind Lonell's Soul Food Cuisine. Family recipes, community roots, and 'A Place of Love' in every dish. Black-owned in South Los Angeles.">
  <div class="min-h-screen pb-16">
    <Section eyebrow="Our Roots" title="'A Place of Love'" description="Lonell's Soul Food Cuisine is more than a restaurant. It's a gathering place built on family recipes, community pride, and the belief that food made with love tastes better." />

    <section class="section-padding bg-[var(--color-surface-card)]">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <picture class="block overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border-subtle)]">
              <source
                srcset="/media/images/dining-bar.webp 1x, /media/images/dining-bar@2x.webp 2x"
                type="image/webp"
              />
              <img
                src="/media/images/dining-bar.jpg"
                alt="Interior of Lonell's Soul Food dining room and bar"
                width="768"
                height="1024"
                class="w-full h-auto object-cover"
                loading="lazy"
              />
            </picture>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <p class="text-base text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed" data-reveal>
              Lonell's Soul Food Cuisine was born from a dream: to share the taste of home with everyone who walked through the door.
              Located in the Vermont Knolls neighborhood of South Los Angeles, Lonell's has become a beloved destination for authentic 
              soul food, live entertainment, and genuine hospitality.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed" data-reveal>
              Every dish tells a story. From the oxtails, slow-cooked until fall-off-the-bone tender, to the fried chicken golden and crisp, 
              to the collard greens simmered with smoked turkey, each recipe carries forward traditions passed down through generations. 
              This is food that nourishes both body and soul.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed" data-reveal>
              What sets Lonell's apart is the marriage of authentic soul food with vibrant live entertainment. 
              Jazz Wednesdays and Fridays, karaoke Saturdays, and Sunday brunch with live music make every visit an experience. 
              Add two private event spaces and a welcoming, casual atmosphere, and you have a true community hub.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed" data-reveal>
              <strong class="text-[var(--color-accent)]">"A Place of Love"</strong> isn't just a tagline. It's our promise. 
              Every guest is treated like family. Every meal is made from scratch. Every visit is an invitation to slow down, 
              connect, and savor something real.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <Section eyebrow="What We Stand For" title="Our Values">
      <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="p-6 bg-[var(--color-surface-card)] rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border-subtle)]">
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Proudly Black-Owned</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">Lonell's is a Black-owned business rooted in South Los Angeles. We honor the culinary traditions of the African American community and contribute to the cultural fabric of our neighborhood.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 bg-[var(--color-surface-card)] rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border-subtle)]">
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Family Recipes</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">Our menu is built on generations of passed-down family recipes. No shortcuts, no compromises. Just honest, made-from-scratch soul food.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 bg-[var(--color-surface-card)] rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border-subtle)]">
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Community First</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">We partner with local organizations, schools, and artists to keep South LA thriving. Our table is your table.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 bg-[var(--color-surface-card)] rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border-subtle)]">
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Live Entertainment</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">We're one of the few soul food restaurants in LA with consistent live entertainment, including jazz, karaoke, and Sunday brunch performances. Dinner and a show, every week.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Section>

    <!-- Location context -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-[var(--color-surface-card)]">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div class="text-center md:text-left">
            <span class="eyebrow" data-reveal>Where We Are</span>
            <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4" data-reveal>Vermont Knolls, South LA</h2>
            <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed" data-reveal>
              Located at 8501 S Vermont Ave in the Vermont Knolls neighborhood of South Los Angeles, an area with 
              deep African American cultural heritage and a thriving community. We're proud to serve this neighborhood 
              and everyone who visits.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-8">
              <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-3 bg-[var(--color-accent)] text-black font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-[var(--color-accent-hover)] transition-colors">
                Find Us
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <picture class="block overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border-subtle)]">
              <source
                srcset="/media/images/street-corner.webp 1x, /media/images/street-corner@2x.webp 2x"
                type="image/webp"
              />
              <img
                src="/media/images/street-corner.jpg"
                alt="Street corner at 85th St and Vermont Ave showing Lonell's Soul Food"
                width="767"
                height="1024"
                class="w-full h-auto object-cover"
                loading="lazy"
              />
            </picture>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
